snippet: The Democratic National Committee plans to vote on a resolution Friday urging Mayor Bob Filner of San Diego to resign.
abstract: Democratic National Committee plans to vote on resolution urging San Diego Mayor Bob Filner to resign amid sexual harassment scandal.
